cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.SY. 

The paper discusses the vulnerabilities in the connected vehicles and proposes a solution using machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of machine learning techniques also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The proposed solution also involves integrating the model as a plug-n-play device in all new and old cars, which suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
